page.title: 02My Day
page.content: I get up at{7.3am},I get dressed then I go to the bathroom and get washed.then I go downstairs and have breakfast.Usually I have Bran Flakes. Just before I go to school I feed my budgie and then I set off for school at{8.35}.I usually walk to school but on Wednesday I go on my bike.I get to school at{9.00am}and go inside the classroom.We have Assembly at{9.15am and come out at{9.45am}.Until playtime we do sums and at playtime I play with Joanna and Clare. After dinner we have art and then playtime is at{2.30.}After play we can choose what we want to do.At{3.30}we leave school.When I get home I go out on my bike.At{7.30}I come in and at {8.30}I go to bed.
